This is the worst result for Black.  If you try to protect the corner by extending at 1 White will protect hiscutting point at 2.  You still need more space to live in the corner so you have to dansu at 3 and then descend at 6, but then White captures the 3 outside Black stones in a net.  This is an awful result for Black.
